        <div class="faq">
            <div class="faq__wrapper">
                <ul class="faq__accord">
                    <li class="faq-item js-accord opened">
                        <button class="faq-item__title js-accord__toggle">How to get started</button>
                        <div class="faq-item__body js-accord__body">
                            <div class="faq-item__body-inner">
                                <p>Click “Get Started” button. After that create new project, setup Stagy on repository. Set settings and then start deploying.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>

                    <li class="faq-item js-accord opened">
                        <button class="faq-item__title js-accord__toggle">Do I need to give access to servers for Stagy?</button>
