                        <div class="faq-item__body js-accord__body">
                            <div class="faq-item__body-inner">
                                <p>The staging server is "as close as possible" copy of the web application production server. It can be used in various situations where owners or users need to do something on production, that should be performed on production. For example to let users or clients to "play" with an application before actual usage. Or test code change before production deployment.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>

